## [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)

### Methods

|                                                                           Method                                                                           |                                                         Return type                                                          |                                          Brief description                                          |
|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| [getId()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#getId())                                                      | `Integer`                                                                                                                    | Returns the unique ID associated with this developer metadata.                                      |
| [getKey()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#getKey())                                                    | `String`                                                                                                                     | Returns the key associated with this developer metadata.                                            |
| [getLocation()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#getLocation())                                          | [DeveloperMetadataLocation](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata-location)     | Returns the location of this developer metadata.                                                    |
| [getValue()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#getValue())                                                | `String`                                                                                                                     | Returns the value associated with this developer metadata, or `null` if this metadata has no value. |
| [getVisibility()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#getVisibility())                                      | [DeveloperMetadataVisibility](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata-visibility) | Returns the visibility of this developer metadata.                                                  |
| [moveToColumn(column)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#moveToColumn(Range))                             | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Moves this developer metadata to the specified column.                                              |
| [moveToRow(row)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#moveToRow(Range))                                      | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Moves this developer metadata to the specified row.                                                 |
| [moveToSheet(sheet)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#moveToSheet(Sheet))                                | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Moves this developer metadata to the specified sheet.                                               |
| [moveToSpreadsheet()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#moveToSpreadsheet())                              | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Moves this developer metadata to the top-level spreadsheet.                                         |
| [remove()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#remove())                                                    | `void`                                                                                                                       | Deletes this metadata.                                                                              |
| [setKey(key)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#setKey(String))                                           | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Sets the key of this developer metadata to the specified value.                                     |
| [setValue(value)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#setValue(String))                                     | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Sets the value associated with this developer metadata to the specified value.                      |
| [setVisibility(visibility)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata#setVisibility(DeveloperMetadataVisibility)) | [DeveloperMetadata](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/spreadsheet/developer-metadata)                      | Sets the visibility of this developer metadata to the specified visibility.                         |
